[[span class="text"]]I have a few ideas.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]Why, do you have any recommendations?[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]]Your guess is as good as mine.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]]You know, typically when people ask me for favors like these they at least try to give me some information to work with.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]Expecting another miracle?[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]]It's what you do best.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]Besides I know you.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]You would've complained if I gave you all the answers.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]]This would've been far easier if you weren't so anal about scrubbing all of our physical intel.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]Figures you'd be the one making my job even harder.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]]You'll be thanking me later.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]It was a necessary evil.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]Imagine if someone like Thirteen had all of those old dossiers. Do you really want someone like him knowing about your personal life?[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]]You say that like it doesn't already apply to you.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]]It doesn't. Not everything atleast.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]And regardless, there's a difference between me having that intel and someone like Thirteen having it.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]]Yeah, I guess.[[/span]]
[[span class="text"]]The other one's not a control freak.[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
